# phase1.5-S5.5 / Stage A — added during multi-instance bring-up.
#
# Without this file, `docker build` drags every `bin/` and `obj/` from
# prior Windows host-side dotnet builds into the build context. Those
# obj/ trees contain MSBuild project.assets.json cache files with
# Windows-only fallback NuGet paths baked in
# (e.g. "C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio\Shared\
# NuGetPackages"), and the Linux SDK inside the container fails
# `dotnet publish` with MSB4018 / "Unable to find fallback package
# folder" because the path does not exist on Linux.
#
# Excluding bin/ and obj/ forces the container to do a clean restore
# from packages.lock and produces a hermetic, reproducible build.

**/bin/
**/obj/

# Test artifacts and IDE state — never needed in a runtime image.
**/TestResults/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# Local environment files / secrets.
**/*.env
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Git metadata — pulled in by the COPY src/ otherwise.
.git/
.gitignore
